title: Easy Clean Extraction Juicer | KitchenAid
description: The KitchenAid® Easy Clean Juicer makes it easy to incorporate fresh fruits and vegetables into your lifestyle. The extra-wide feed tube lets you add whole fruits and vegetables, and the ceramic slicing dish reduces buildup and extracts more liquid. Learn more about possibilities, performance, and easy juicing capabilities.
